334
00:37:15,266 --> 00:37:17,359
So they throw him in a lake.

335
00:37:17,435 --> 00:37:20,893
All depends, Henry,
on how you look at it.

336
00:37:20,972 --> 00:37:25,136
Either you're halfway to heaven
or halfway to hell.

337
00:37:25,209 --> 00:37:27,734
Here we go, Father.

338
00:37:27,812 --> 00:37:29,746
