I know.

360
00:39:42,813 --> 00:39:44,246
...from now on

361
00:39:44,315 --> 00:39:45,577
They heard of me...

362
00:39:45,649 --> 00:39:47,583
This is going
to be difficult.

363
00:39:47,651 --> 00:39:49,915
...about the past

364
00:39:49,987 --> 00:39:51,420
Yep.

365
00:39:51,489 --> 00:39:53,923
Now I don't care if I'm...

366
00:39:53,991 --> 00:39:58,621
Ever since we started
moving folks out...

367
00:39:58,696 --> 00:40:00,095
we've never done well

368
00:40:00,164 --> 00:40:01,756
with people
that owned Chevrolets.

369
00:40:01,832 --> 00:40:02,764
...I'll be the last.

370
00:40:02,833 --> 00:40:04,357
Matt...

371
00:40:07,838 --> 00:40:12,298
...this country is being divided
into two types of people...

372
00:40:14,278 --> 00:40:16,940
Chevy people...

373
00:40:19,817 --> 00:40:21,580
...and Ford people, Matt.

374
00:40:23,687 --> 00:40:25,314
Yep.

375
00:40:32,363 --> 00:40:35,457
Now, I don't care

376
00:40:35,533 --> 00:40:40,971
If I'm not the first love
you've known

377
00:40:41,038 --> 00:40:46,305
Just so I'll be the last

378
00:40:46,377 --> 00:40:49,403
Now, I don't care...

379
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:53,416
Looks like he got
some kind of hammer.

