Once again, selfish.

388
00:41:32,990 --> 00:41:34,855
How observant.

389
00:41:34,925 --> 00:41:37,485
The noble Englishman.

390
00:41:37,561 --> 00:41:41,292
How I longed to be Earl Grey.

391
00:41:41,365 --> 00:41:44,198
The wit that got us here.

392
00:41:44,268 --> 00:41:46,964
It's a splendid
acquisition.

393
00:41:47,037 --> 00:41:48,436
Unknown architect.

394
00:41:48,506 --> 00:41:50,565
Probably owner-builder.

395
00:41:50,641 --> 00:41:53,235
A true visionary,
I might add.

396
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:54,242
Jesus.

397
00:41:54,311 --> 00:41:58,716
No, no, he was a carpenter.

398
00:41:58,782 --> 00:42:00,977
We-we-we're searching
for the unknown.

399
00:42:01,051 --> 00:42:04,919
The unknown doesn't just
come knocking on your door.

400
00:42:04,989 --> 00:42:09,926
If it is unknown, how would you
know if it did come knocking?

401
00:42:10,060 --> 00:42:13,496
Well, it won't be
in the shape of a child.

402
00:42:13,564 --> 00:42:14,929
I would have to agree.

403
00:42:15,032 --> 00:42:16,499
Happy.

404
00:42:16,567 --> 00:42:19,263
Do you ever disagree?

405
00:42:19,336 --> 00:42:24,069
I disagree with
the Englishman's use of starch.

406
00:42:26,110 --> 00:42:29,409
What do the Scriptures say?

407
00:42:32,316 --> 00:42:35,717
"Temperature, 105 degrees.
High.

408
00:42:35,786 --> 00:42:39,483
Please look after him
when I leave."

409
00:42:53,170 --> 00:42:55,400
What do you suppose we do?

410
00:42:55,472 --> 00:42:58,464
We're going to wing it.

411
00:43:50,361 --> 00:43:51,953
It appears they've...

412
00:43:52,062 --> 00:43:54,656
worn out their welcome.

413
00:44:02,573 --> 00:44:03,835
Good afternoon, Mr. Stalling.

414
00:44:03,907 --> 00:44:05,101
My name is Walter O'Brien.

415
00:44:05,175 --> 00:44:06,403
This here's my son, Willis.

416
00:44:06,477 --> 00:44:08,104
We're with
the evacuation committee.

417
00:44:08,178 --> 00:44:09,645
It's been brought
to the state's attention

418
00:44:09,713 --> 00:44:11,044
that you are seeking
some assistance.

419
00:44:11,115 --> 00:44:12,605
