asked us to come to your aid.

422
00:44:16,153 --> 00:44:17,552
The state understands
your difficulty

423
00:44:17,621 --> 00:44:18,918
with moving on.

424
00:44:19,056 --> 00:44:21,854
The state
will not hurt, destroy,

425
00:44:21,925 --> 00:44:25,793
nor harm you physically
in any way.

426
00:44:25,863 --> 00:44:31,392
It is our civil duty to assist
you in making this transition

427
00:44:31,468 --> 00:44:35,370
as easy and pleasant
as possible.

428
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:45,748
Your agreement is this...

429
00:44:45,816 --> 00:44:50,048
you will each be assigned
65 households to depart.

430
00:44:50,120 --> 00:44:53,214
Having fulfilled
said obligation,

431
00:44:53,290 --> 00:44:57,249
you will then
each receive 1.5 acres

432
00:44:57,327 --> 00:45:01,423
of prime, lakefront property.

433
00:45:01,498 --> 00:45:03,830
Your lot size
will be increased

434
00:45:03,901 --> 00:45:06,369
by one fifth of an acre
for every additional household

435
00:45:06,437 --> 00:45:10,066
that you assist in evacuating
beyond the initial 65.

436
00:45:10,140 --> 00:45:13,234
Have I made myself clear?

437
00:45:19,650 --> 00:45:22,551
I will take your vacant
stares as a yes.

438
00:45:25,622 --> 00:45:28,318
I could live
with an acre and a half.

439
00:45:29,426 --> 00:45:32,020
Okay by me.

440
00:45:35,999 --> 00:45:37,091
May we, sir?

441
00:45:57,421 --> 00:45:58,911
So...

442
00:46:01,325 --> 00:46:03,623
...the prodigal son returns.

443
00:46:03,694 --> 00:46:05,889
Already packed.

444
00:46:05,963 --> 00:46:08,261
A little ahead of yourself.

445
00:46:08,332 --> 00:46:10,391
I've brought
what you're looking for.

446
00:46:10,467 --> 00:46:12,594
You have?

447
00:46:12,669 --> 00:46:14,933
Outside.

448
00:46:21,578 --> 00:46:23,478
I don't see anything.

449
00:46:23,547 --> 00:46:24,479
We still have a deal?

450
00:46:24,548 --> 00:46:25,139
Yes, yes, yes.

451
00:46:25,215 --> 00:46:26,739
We have a deal.

452
00:46:28,385 --> 00:46:31,912
Yeah, we still have a deal.

453
00:46:32,022 --> 00:46:34,650
Where is it?

454
00:46:40,597 --> 00:46:42,827
Oh, my.

455
00:46:59,183 --> 00:47:00,844
Hello.

456
00:47:29,947 --> 00:47:31,881
We'd appreciate it

457
00:47:31,949 --> 00:47:33,780
if you both would stop

458
00:47:33,851 --> 00:47:35,944
screwing around.

459
00:47:43,727 --> 00:47:45,786
Well, what do you want to do?

460
00:47:45,863 --> 00:47:49,026
The Youngs are going
to have a moving sale.

461
00:47:49,099 --> 00:47:50,964
Perfect.

462
00:47:55,706 --> 00:47:57,037
Now, all I need is a pair

463
00:47:57,107 --> 00:47:58,404
of sinners like yourselves

464
00:47:58,475 --> 00:47:59,407
to mount up there now.

465
00:47:59,476 --> 00:47:59,942
We appreciate

466
00:48:00,077 --> 00:48:01,169
very much your giving us

467
00:48:01,245 --> 00:48:03,236
this time to discuss
this matter.

468
00:48:04,815 --> 00:48:06,009
A pair of wives?

469
00:48:06,083 --> 00:48:07,175
At least they're not mounted.

470
00:48:07,251 --> 00:48:08,183
You know,

471
00:48:08,252 --> 00:48:09,685
it appears to me
that you folks

472
00:48:09,753 --> 00:48:12,153
are preparing for a flood
in Biblical proportions.

473
00:48:12,222 --> 00:48:13,553
You got that right, son.

474
00:48:13,624 --> 00:48:16,024
A flood is going to wipe
through this place,

475
00:48:16,093 --> 00:48:17,754
cleansing the soil of all sin.

476
00:48:17,828 --> 00:48:19,557
Understandable.

477
00:48:19,630 --> 00:48:21,257
When God tells us
to get a move on,

478
00:48:21,331 --> 00:48:23,424
we're gone at the first holler
of a rooster.

479
00:48:23,500 --> 00:48:25,365
We ain't needing the State
to come in here

480
00:48:25,435 --> 00:48:27,335
and tell us when
to pick up and get going.

481
00:48:27,404 --> 00:48:28,371
That's God's doing.

482
00:48:28,438 --> 00:48:32,898
This is God's land,
and by God,

483
00:48:32,976 --> 00:48:38,004
we ain't movin' until we get
that sign from above.

484
00:48:38,081 --> 00:48:39,207
Yes, sir, uh...

485
00:48:39,283 --> 00:48:41,513
we aren't telling you
to pick up and get going.

486
00:48:41,585 --> 00:48:42,643
No, sir.

487
00:48:42,719 --> 00:48:44,914
Look at us as your
life preservers.

488
00:48:44,988 --> 00:48:46,478
You can use us if you want,

489
00:48:46,556 --> 00:48:47,488
or not at all.

490
00:48:47,557 --> 00:48:48,922
We give you that choice.

491
00:48:48,992 --> 00:48:50,550
We're all in the same boat.

492
00:48:50,627 --> 00:48:52,561
So, sir, if you
don't mind, sir,

493
00:48:52,629 --> 00:48:55,291
